Questar is a role playing game modeled after Rogue, Angband and Nethack. It
was written as a learning exercise for C# and .NET. The game was never
completed or intended to be.

Questar is written in C#/.NET using the Mono .NET implementation. It uses GTK#
UI Toolkit and Cairo for drawing. Game data is stored as XML and accessed LINQ
query expressions.

